review_reason: Plan v004 Phase 1 blocked: the generalized_forward_temporal_witness_seed_consistent lemma is mathematically false. Independent analysis confirmed the counterexample: GContent(M) subset N does not prevent G(neg(psi)) from entering N via Lindenbaum, making {psi} union GContent(N) inconsistent. Research-004 Section 3.3 reached the same conclusion. All subsequent phases (2-5) depend on this lemma. A new plan (v005) is needed.
